 programming paradigms and runs on the Java Virtual Machine. It offers concise syntax, pattern matching, and actor-based concurrency through Akka.", "Lua is a lightweight, embeddable scripting language designed for extensibility and performance in video games and embedded systems. It features a simple syntax, automatic memory management, and first-class functions."], "scores": [0.5975972004586377, 0.3966407175720845, 0.388790802658077, 0.356941460312286, 0.35434886239471497], "model_name": "mpnet", "document_ids": ["Python", "Haskell", "Perl", "Scala", "Lua"]}}